    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but if we call an ambulance it's going to be a whole huge thing and it's so expensive here. plus he's literally saying he feels fine once he sits down. can't we just give him some aspirin and some water and monitor him for an hour to see if the tingling goes away? if it's just jet lag it'll fix itself with sleep and hydration.",
