      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Do not give aspirin, as it can worsen bleeding if the cause is a bleed rather than a clot, and absolutely do not wait to see if symptoms resolve. These are the exact signs of a stroke, and every minute counts for a chance at recovery at a hospital, where they can save your dad's life and prevent permanent brain damage. Even if he feels better later, the window for treatment is so narrow that waiting an hour at home is dangerous and could result in severe disability or death. Please call emergency services immediately to get professional help now.",
